records.nl_statement: Let $V$ be a vector space over an infinite field $F$. Show that $V$ cannot be the set-theoretic union of a finite number of proper subspaces of $V$.
records.lean_header:
import Mathlib

open Fintype Set Real Ideal Polynomial
open scoped BigOperators
records.ground_truth:
